４. Notes

ᠰᠡᠴᠡᠨ	Сэчэн is normally ᠴᠡᠴᠡᠨ цэцэн in Mongolia. (Back)
ᠰᠢᠬᠢᠷ	Шихэр is normally pronounced чихэр in Mongolia. (Back)
ᠣᠴᠢᠷ	In IM, ᠣᠴᠢᠷ ʊʧɪr / учир is used as an equivalent of Chinese 事
shì or 事情 shìqing, 'a matter to attend to'. In M it appears to be mainly
used in the meaning 'reason, cause, meaning'. (Back)
Pronunciation differences continue to make themselves apparent.

1. ᠬᠦᠦ ᠡᠴᠡ ᠪᠠᠨ is pronounced xu:gə:sə̌n as opposed to хүүгээсээ in Mongolia.

2. Rather surprisingly, ᠬᠦᠦ ᠨᠢ was pronounced xu:gə̌n by the teacher where хүү нь
is normal in Mongolia.
